# Format: TOON
# Goal: Define standard plumbing fixtures, pipe sizes, and precise wet-area layouts.
# Reference: Standard sizes (Kohler/Jaquar/Grohe specs) and CPVC/PVC pipe norms.

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 1. PIPE & FITTING STANDARDS
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
PlumbingLineType[List]{code, description, material, standard_dia_mm, color_code}:
  L-COLD | Cold Water Supply | CPVC | 20, 25, 32 | White/Yellow_Stripe
  L-HOT | Hot Water Supply | CPVC_Heavy | 20, 25 | Red_Stripe
  L-DRN-GRY | Grey Water Drain (Sink/Shower/AC) | PVC | 40, 50, 75 | Grey
  L-DRN-BLK | Black Water Drain (WC) | PVC | 110 | Grey
  L-VENT | Vent Pipe | PVC | 50, 75 | Grey

