  FIX-SH-Overhead | Shower | Wall_Arm_Output | 2100 | -
  FIX-SH-Spout | Shower | Wall_Spout_Output | 750 | -
  # BASIN
  FIX-WB-Counter | Basin | Bottle_Trap_Wall | 450 (Drain) | 32
  FIX-WB-Tap | Tap | Pillar_Cock / Wall_Mixer | 1050 (Wall) / 850 (Counter) | -
  # WC (COMMODE)
  FIX-WC-WallHung | Commode | Concealed_Tank_Inlet | 1000 (Tank Center) | 110
